This is how to longest of strings:
   When strings's length is 0, then:
      The answer is []
   End when
   Remember that best is item 0 in strings
   Remember that bestlen is best's length
   Remember that n is strings's length
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that s is item i in strings
      Remember that len is s's length
      When len is more than bestlen, then:
         Remember that best is s
         Remember that bestlen is len
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
